        public void setCallbackClasses​(Set<String> callbackClasses)
        Sets the class names of callbacks. hese are the callback classes defined by the Android SDK, and they are not mapped to the current application. If this value is null, FlowDroid automatically loads the names from AndroidCallbacks.txt as the default behavior.
        Parameters:
        callbackClasses - The class names of callbacks or null to use the default file.
